Lines
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Baseline                The line where the characters sit
X-Height                The height from the baseline to the top of the lowercase x
Cap Line                The height of the uppercase letters
Ascent Line             The furthest possible distance the characters can go up
Descent Line            The furthest possible distance the characters can go down
Line Height/Leading     The distance between the ascent and descent lines               {line-height: 1.5rem;}
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
Text Blocks
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Kerning                 The space between the letters
Ligatures               Combinations of certain characters
Measure/Text Width      66 characters is ideal
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
 
Fonts
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Serif                   Characters with decoration
Sans Serif              Characters without decoration
